For Task 1, I created a Digital Literacy Awareness infographic using Canva. The aim of this task was to highlight the importance of digital literacy for students in today’s digital world.

The infographic covers key topics such as online safety, useful digital tools, and email etiquette. It presents information in a simple and visually appealing way using icons, headings, and short bullet points.

This task helped me understand how to communicate important information effectively through design. It also improved my creativity and awareness about safe and responsible use of digital technologies.

